com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FJokGNK.html&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1d280f7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/JokGNK.html</a>"},{"pid":"ee3419d4e5c86860f33c0053115a23212567cdfd","tid":339531,"uid":22365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T11:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://read01.com/JokGNK.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FJokGNK.html&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1d280f7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/JokGNK.html</a></blockquote><br />\n1、鳳梨的葉子比較光滑，不帶鋸齒<br />\n<br />\n2、鳳梨的肉刺比較淺，削皮即食<br />\n<br />\n3、鳳梨不用泡鹽水就可以直接吃<br />\n<br />\n聽起來頭頭是道是不是？但我要告訴你的是，這純屬一本正經的胡說八道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/JokGNK.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FJokGNK.html&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1d280f7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/JokGNK.html</a>"},{"pid":"152714792c35aaac2a1f0046cd0a546439133666","tid":339531,"uid":71954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T11:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://read01.com/JokGNK.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FJokGNK.html&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1d280f7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/JokGNK.html</a></blockquote><br />\n1、鳳梨的葉子比較光滑，不帶鋸齒<br />\n<br />\n2、鳳梨的肉刺比較淺，削皮即食<br />\n<br />\n3、鳳梨不用泡鹽水就可以直接吃<br />\n<br />\n聽起來頭頭是道是不是？但我要告訴你的是，這純屬一本正經的胡說八道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/JokGNK.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FJokGNK.html&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1d280f7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/JokGNK.html</a></blockquote><br />\n只要識分 哈林 同 庾澄慶<br />\n就會自然分到 菠蘿 同 鳳梨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /